OL,3,CMan charged with possession of a
OL,4,Cfirearm following incident in Barry
OL,6,FA man has been charged with possession
OL,7,Fof a firearm following an incident on
OL,8,FPark Road in Barry.
OL,10,F18-year-old Dominic Bily from
OL,11,FLlanrumney in Cardiff has been charged
OL,12,Fwith possession of a firearm with
OL,13,Fintent to cause fear of violence.
OL,15,FThe incident took place at around
OL,16,F10:30pm on Monday 13 April.
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police were called to Park
OL,19,FRoad after reports of 'loud bangs' and
OL,20,Fthat a person had been assaulted.
OL,21,FHowever, no victims have come forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
