OL,3,CMan charged with possession of a
OL,4,Cfirearm following incident in Barry
OL,6,FEnquiries are continuing and checks
OL,7,Fhave been made with local hospitals,
OL,8,Fbut as yet no victims have been
OL,9,Fidentified.
OL,11,FDominic Bily appeared at Cardiff
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday 15
OL,13,FApril and has been remanded in custody.
OL,15,FA 17-year-old boy from Canton, also
OL,16,Farrested in connection with the
OL,17,Fincident, has been released on police
OL,18,Fbail pending further enquiries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
